long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:

• Shortcuts 
• Auto Sniper Bot
• Auto Bid Bot
• Sell with one key 
• Futbin SBC importer 
• Futbin prices

And many other features that will help you make tons of credits every day!
